>This error usually occurs, if you opened too many files within various
>REXX-scripts due to some faulty REXX-program (that's at least what had happened
>to me). Doing a reboot helped in my case, fixing the REXX-program and since
>then never had such a problem again.
>
>---rony
>

If that's the problem, make sure that all your REXX programs close the
files that they open...

open:   text = linein("C:\FILE")

close:  call stream "C:\FILE", "C", "CLOSE"

